  "title": "Relationship Manager (Private Wealth Management)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Source for and acquire new client within market, develop long-term solutions for the clients</li><li>Understanding client’s business and sources of wealth generation, as well as client’s financial and investment goals in creation and management of their wealth</li><li>Provide tailored solution that address client’s investment risk management and financiering / liquidity need</li><li>Provide quality and efficient after-sales service</li><li>Responsible for achieving annual targets and agreed service standards</li><li>Ensure compliance with all regulations and controls as by the company and external regulatory authorities</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree with at least 5 years’ experience in serving high net worth clients; exposure to Taiwanese Market will be advantageous </li><li>Understand and able to apply compliance and regulatory requirements</li><li>Good private wealth product knowledge</li><li>A holder of Singapore client advisory competency standards (CACS) qualification</li><li>Strong client facing sales and stakeholder management skills<br /></li></ul><p>Ready to make an impact? We’d love to hear from you! Apply today by sending your resume to <strong>apply81@talentvis.com </strong>or <strong>click apply now!</strong><br /></p><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified<br /></p><p>Talentvis Singapore Pte Ltd | EA License No: 04C3537</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Sherwin Wong | EA Personnel No: R1770151</p>",
